                <div class="div-line"></div>
                <p>Thanks to digital India initiatives, the RC transfer process has become easier and faster through online portals like Parivahan. In this 2025 step-by-step guide by <span class="font-weight-700"><a class="for-link" asp-controller="Home" asp-action="Index">BikeCarHub</a></span>, we explain how to transfer RC for second-hand vehicles efficiently, legally, and conveniently.</p>

