                <h2 class="subheading">Why RC Transfer is Necessary</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Legal ownership proof for the buyer</li>
                    <li>Protects seller from future traffic fines or legal issues</li>
                    <li>Required for insurance claim settlement</li>
