                    <li>After the sale of a used vehicle (bike or car)</li>
                    <li>Within-family transfers (gift or inheritance)</li>
                    <li>Ownership change due to the death of the owner</li>
                    <li>Inter-state relocation and registration change</li>
                </ul>

                <div class="div-line"></div>
                <h2 class="subheading">RC Transfer Scenarios</h2>
