                    <li>Enter Application Number and Date of Birth</li>
                    <li>View real-time status: pending, under review, approved, dispatched</li>
                </ol>

                <div class="div-line"></div>
                <h2 class="subheading">Common Mistakes to Avoid</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Failing to check pending challans</li>
                    <li>Missing NOC in case of inter-state transfer</li>
                    <li>Not updating insurance to buyer's name</li>
                    <li>Uploading poor quality or incorrect documents</li>
                    <li>Delaying submission post-sale</li>
                </ul>

                <div class="div-line"></div>
                <h2 class="subheading">Tips for Smooth RC Transfer</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>Always use high-resolution scanned documents</li>
                    <li>Choose weekdays for RTO appointments</li>
                    <li>Maintain backup copies of receipts and forms</li>
                    <li>Start the process within 14 days of sale</li>
                </ul>

